  <h1>Hey Friends</h1><div>Thanks for following along.&nbsp; Or checking in sometime later in the future.&nbsp; Or hey future Truman or Carrie reminiscing about what will hopefully be beautiful and fun trip.&nbsp; Or if this is an artifact that's discovered in some apocalypse future, well, I hope you're alright and can lay your hands on some bottle caps or whatever is the currency du jour.<br><br>What will follow here is a brief accounting of our trip out west to get married in Yosemite.&nbsp; Brief because I'm typing this after driving all day, and because my laptop's dumb butterfly keyboard keeps sticking my "T"s, and because I have the utmost care for my dear readers' time and attention.<br><br><action-text-attachment sgid="BAh7CEkiCGdpZAY6BkVUSSJXZ2lkOi8vYW4tZXZlbnQvQWN0aXZlU3RvcmFnZTo6QmxvYi9jOWYyMjM5NS0yMzhmLTQwZjQtODMxZC05ZmUzM2E1ZDlhZmQ_ZXhwaXJlc19pbgY7AFRJIgxwdXJwb3NlBjsAVEkiD2F0dGFjaGFibGUGOwBUSSIPZXhwaXJlc19hdAY7AFQw--74290b3f620ad147af98acb9506838abad47ef8f" content-type="image/jpeg" url="https://www.carrie-truman.fyi/rails/active_storage/blobs/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaEpJaWxqT1dZeU1qTTVOUzB5TXpobUxUUXdaalF0T0RNeFpDMDVabVV6TTJFMVpEbGhabVFHT2daRlZBPT0iLCJleHAiOm51bGwsInB1ciI6ImJsb2JfaWQifX0=--a6aadc8fffcc05923ebded863efd29577481d1b0/IMG_2599.jpg" filename="IMG_2599.jpg" filesize="152732" width="640" height="853" previewable="true" presentation="gallery" caption="Hey I can add pictures to these things.  Pretty neat!"><figure class="attachment attachment--preview attachment--jpg">
