</div><div><br></div><h1>Packing</h1><div>We spent some time packing up over the last week or so.&nbsp; Mostly throwing camping things in a bin, figuring out how to transport all of our costco peanut m&amp;ms, and wrangling all of the generous presents that folks sent (thank you so much, generally -- and a much more personal thanks forthcoming after we return home).<br><br>We also put some Nutzo in squeeze pouches, and worked through a long packing list, and tried not to check the Yosemite air quality index too often.&nbsp; Carrie's mom came to visit the last weekend before we left and brought a helpful guide to writing vows.&nbsp; It recommends several times to get started a few months in advance but, uh, oh well.<br><br><action-text-attachment sgid="BAh7CEkiCGdpZAY6BkVUSSJXZ2lkOi8vYW4tZXZlbnQvQWN0aXZlU3RvcmFnZTo6QmxvYi84ZGZmMmY2Yi0yMWI3LTRjMWEtOGZhZi0xYWYwODlkNmNmZWQ_ZXhwaXJlc19pbgY7AFRJIgxwdXJwb3NlBjsAVEkiD2F0dGFjaGFibGUGOwBUSSIPZXhwaXJlc19hdAY7AFQw--bd02e063324b4c27d6ca8aa005b3d26b85ce57bd" content-type="image/jpeg" url="https://www.carrie-truman.fyi/rails/active_storage/blobs/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaEpJaWs0WkdabU1tWTJZaTB5TVdJM0xUUmpNV0V0T0daaFppMHhZV1l3T0Rsa05tTm1aV1FHT2daRlZBPT0iLCJleHAiOm51bGwsInB1ciI6ImJsb2JfaWQifX0=--4673349b44aa5d9983b89e9402ebd8ef33113ae8/IMG_2603.jpg" filename="IMG_2603.jpg" filesize="117410" width="640" height="480" previewable="true" presentation="gallery" caption="This will be us in Death Valley, with hopefully the same number of scorpions."><figure class="attachment attachment--preview attachment--jpg">
