</figure></action-text-attachment><br><br>We're really hoping to be able to snag either a backcountry permit, or an unclaimed reservation at Phantom Ranch at the bottom of the grand canyon.&nbsp; Who knows if that will happen, but we decided to prepare some backpacking meals just in case we're able to hike down.&nbsp; Carrie found what look to be <a href="https://www.theyummylife.com/Backpacking_Food">some great recipes</a>, which we sort of followed.&nbsp; We're hoping to spend two nights down there because the hiking part seems pretty difficult and a little intimidating.<br><br> <action-text-attachment sgid="BAh7CEkiCGdpZAY6BkVUSSJXZ2lkOi8vYW4tZXZlbnQvQWN0aXZlU3RvcmFnZTo6QmxvYi9iMzExMzIwMi02MTkxLTQ0NTctOTQzNC1jMWVmOGYyNTIzMDI_ZXhwaXJlc19pbgY7AFRJIgxwdXJwb3NlBjsAVEkiD2F0dGFjaGFibGUGOwBUSSIPZXhwaXJlc19hdAY7AFQw--510bc222261786be829ba30766822ee67ff469ed" content-type="image/jpeg" url="https://www.carrie-truman.fyi/rails/active_storage/blobs/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaEpJaWxpTXpFeE16SXdNaTAyTVRreExUUTBOVGN0T1RRek5DMWpNV1ZtT0dZeU5USXpNRElHT2daRlZBPT0iLCJleHAiOm51bGwsInB1ciI6ImJsb2JfaWQifX0=--645788c6a512c7477383f22d222f174c484492b9/IMG_2614.jpg" filename="IMG_2614.jpg" filesize="124269" width="640" height="480" previewable="true" presentation="gallery" caption="&quot;Future Essentials&quot; speaks of a grim imagining of what the future may hold.  We'll let you know how it tastes in the more immediate future, later."><figure class="attachment attachment--preview attachment--jpg">
