</div><div><br></div><h1>Setting Out</h1><div>We set out this morning at eight -- having planned for seven, only dropping an hour is a pretty big win.&nbsp; Our first day will bring us to Bristow, Oklahoma (we originally planned for Oklahoma City, but decided to cut an hour) by way of St. Louis.&nbsp; Expect some breathtaking photography of the Arch later on.<br><br><action-text-attachment sgid="BAh7CEkiCGdpZAY6BkVUSSJXZ2lkOi8vYW4tZXZlbnQvQWN0aXZlU3RvcmFnZTo6QmxvYi9kZTA1MGY3Ny1iNzhmLTRiOTAtYWM5OS1kMDgxYmUxM2EyODc_ZXhwaXJlc19pbgY7AFRJIgxwdXJwb3NlBjsAVEkiD2F0dGFjaGFibGUGOwBUSSIPZXhwaXJlc19hdAY7AFQw--2f7cb27acd923627759ae34481bd786abee15c62" content-type="image/jpeg" url="https://www.carrie-truman.fyi/rails/active_storage/blobs/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaEpJaWxrWlRBMU1HWTNOeTFpTnpobUxUUmlPVEF0WVdNNU9TMWtNRGd4WW1VeE0yRXlPRGNHT2daRlZBPT0iLCJleHAiOm51bGwsInB1ciI6ImJsb2JfaWQifX0=--3a61c4c7d57aba635bede7c5f0b5ff4244d1e34e/IMG_2666.jpg" filename="IMG_2666.jpg" filesize="122262" width="640" height="480" previewable="true" presentation="gallery" caption="The mighty, rugged Prius is just about full up."><figure class="attachment attachment--preview attachment--jpg">
    <img src="{% imageUrl 'src/images/IMG_2666.jpg' %}">

  <figcaption class="attachment__caption">
      The mighty, rugged Prius is just about full up.
  </figcaption>
</figure></action-text-attachment><br><br>I'm grateful to be able to go on this trip, and grateful for the love and support from all of you.&nbsp; I'm looking forward to stepping away from my day-to-day life for a couple of weeks, to be getting married -- and saving on health insurance, which was literally part of Carrie's marriage pitch late last year.&nbsp; We've been together for very-almost ten years, so practicalities sometimes speak up first.&nbsp; But I did use every one of the eighteen candles that we have floating around our house to later do a real proposal, so not all romance is dead.&nbsp; <br><br> Anyway, hopefully we can all hang out soon.&nbsp; Thanks for your time, and for your attention.<br><br><action-text-attachment sgid="BAh7CEkiCGdpZAY6BkVUSSJXZ2lkOi8vYW4tZXZlbnQvQWN0aXZlU3RvcmFnZTo6QmxvYi9lZDViYjBiMS04N2VhLTQyODUtOGJlYS1mODY2MDJmZDI5NjE_ZXhwaXJlc19pbgY7AFRJIgxwdXJwb3NlBjsAVEkiD2F0dGFjaGFibGUGOwBUSSIPZXhwaXJlc19hdAY7AFQw--3f66fb2bd52b192df5cc780982e4f71120bb307c" content-type="image/jpeg" url="https://www.carrie-truman.fyi/rails/active_storage/blobs/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaEpJaWxsWkRWaVlqQmlNUzA0TjJWaExUUXlPRFV0T0dKbFlTMW1PRFkyTURKbVpESTVOakVHT2daRlZBPT0iLCJleHAiOm51bGwsInB1ciI6ImJsb2JfaWQifX0=--096d9a3743870153d1d27148ceb1edeea9ea7d19/IMG_2668.jpg" filename="IMG_2668.jpg" filesize="156189" width="640" height="853" previewable="true" presentation="gallery" caption="Thanks also to Caroline, for this great (chocolate!) banana bread breakfast."><figure class="attachment attachment--preview attachment--jpg">
